filetype plugin indent on
" to turn syntax highlighting on, and show the file name in the terminal title bar
syn on se title
" Kernel options:
set tabstop=8
set softtabstop=8
set shiftwidth=8
set noexpandtab

" Userspace options:
" show existing tab with 4 spaces width
" set tabstop=4
" when indenting with '>', use 4 spaces width
" set shiftwidth=4
" On pressing tab, insert 4 spaces
" set expandtab

" Allow saving of files as sudo when I forgot to start vim using sudo.
cmap w!! w !sudo tee > /dev/null %

